{"tid":2510304,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"冷門漫畫推介「歷經弦音」，發出心中靈魂的吶喊","createTime":"2021-04-30T05:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T05:49:00.000Z","uid":235939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"26a9c92d4402dfafebf1a7c47f4e191d5434c849","tid":2510304,"uid":235939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:35:09.000Z","msg":"歷經弦音<br />\n一套獻給係現實同追夢中掙扎的人嘅漫畫<br />\n<br />\n<strong>故事簡介</strong><br />\n女主角紫織係一名平凡土氣嘅高中老師，某一日比結他之神Jimi Hendrix嘅鬼魂纏上左；通過同佢「jack in」，jimi可以「上身」落女主到彈出高超嘅結他solo。但「jack in」過嘅人如果係27歲之前未能創造音樂傳說就會死去，此為「27歲的詛咒」。而為左生存、更為左重拾過去嘅夢想，主角決定要組織一隊可以創造傳說嘅樂隊出黎。<br />\n而jimi之於女主就好似佐為之於進藤光，但比起直接「上身」，jimi更常係扮演指導者嘅角色。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXjC49ZkVzZuEN3tTe7dhS3KXEYnryFh1sh7PzXSqwoih?filename=D2wKs3H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2wKs3H.png&h=4212714c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以睇得出故事嘅設定好明顯參考左藍調始祖Robert Johnson &rsquo;crossroad devil&rsquo; 都市傳聞同埋音樂界著名嘅 &lsquo;27 club&rsquo; 傳說。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>成人嘅夢想</strong><br />\n如果你係一個成年人甚至係出左社會嘅成年人，就會明白究竟追逐夢想係有幾困難，旁人嘅譏笑、自己嘅無能、生活層面/習慣嘅阻礙。<br />\n比較「理想化」d嘅漫畫通常會講到主角冇咩爭扎好輕鬆咁破解呢d困難，或者好單純咁話其實其他人嘅嘲笑只係佢地唔知主角幾鬼勁，主角後來一發威就即刻「打臉」佢地，雖然睇得好爽但同現實相去甚遠。係呢套漫畫入面，好多旁人嘅嘲笑/冷言冷語都唔係誤解，而反而真係直接點出左主角團嘅真實問題：練習不足、過於遷就團員導致作品四不像、成員之間實力差距大、「呢度冇人識你啊」太唔出名<br />\n你會見到漫畫入面嘅角色好似真人夾band咁面對各款難題，有要團體一齊面對嘅，亦有必須要自己一個獨自面對，睇完之後你應該會明白點解現實中會有咁多隊band解散<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係每一次嘅失落難過都會變成前進嘅動力，因為所謂嘅藝術家，就係感受越深就越容易創作出名作嘅奇怪生物<br />\n<br />\n每一次嘅solo都係靈魂嘅吶喊<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQqNSEvGdcezZKBSrddRGyBRc9pwmg7nbcFijUjbvnW5r?filename=4DgOaAE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4DgOaAE.png&h=68a65079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>情感描寫</strong><br />\n呢套野入面對角色嘅心理描寫都可以用「細膩」黎形容；我經常會將呢套野同另一套漫畫「衝鋒21」作對比，兩者都係「競技類」漫畫，兩者都對唔同角色嘅背景/心理有深入詳盡嘅描寫，讀者會理解到唔同人點解會作出咁嘅決定、點解會變成宜家嘅佢，從而對角色產生共鳴甚至好感。<br />\n唔同角色之間嘅互動火花都好高質，一d你原先以為毫無關聯嘅人物都可以刷出一d你意想不到嘅化學反應<br />\n最重要嘅係，佢同「衝鋒21」一樣<strong><span class=\"red\">熱血到爆</span></strong>!<br />\n<br />\n<strong>分鏡/畫面</strong><br />\n除左情感上嘅描寫，講到呢套野不得不提嘅就係佢嘅「分鏡」同埋「畫面衝擊力」，係冇聲音嘅漫畫到要呈現音樂嘅衝擊力其實係極之考驗作者功力嘅。呢套漫畫被稱為「有聲音嘅漫畫」，唔係講緊佢用擬聲詞去模擬or旁人嘅形容去講解d音樂有幾正，而係佢簡單直接咁用分鏡/畫面去比你「感受」到果種衝擊力。下面舉一兩個例子<br />\n<br />\njimi同nirvana主唱Kurt Cobain合唱<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmc7p8oTPevH43BAj592NFcw7ycDN9sQJHz9QHBUZptZr9?filename=m42mvuv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm42mvuv.png&h=9cca5cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYugZfMXidb1A6BaRoxmArz4Jvy1cLdX3hsQTceoGoURV?filename=N1mZg9u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1mZg9u.png&h=011b342f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT3mc5T9rrBEEkzJCwAtS6GYSax555HNE5EZYyuV8C1wk?filename=d8G6GA8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8G6GA8.png&h=87ab1ec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV5wF3DxUZ9Q6Sng1hf4dGbVh8Dbo2s2Evuv4ocymy5dX?filename=xzNQ8f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxzNQ8f8.png&h=13a91f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZnCes7WfwbvSBCUYSf4CkGUYanJkC4vGshvxrJ8o9AKE?filename=ZQAZ1A7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQAZ1A7.png&h=f904992d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmafBUQCXwZVz4yeccN1i7pTdCgvXmFs6DvaFLCpdYHaBG?filename=2evfzV6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2evfzV6.png&h=a1d05aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主角經歷崩潰後發出嘅靈魂吶喊(solo)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXSX3FNGEeGjVWPnAhKBYvTjLbEKbiMiPuoN7DZHCaMcx?filename=BL40Mip.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBL40Mip.png&h=a752cbd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU3LXTszARozYLw1NF3pRByjWqAZJUVrtZN7MPmZZj5A2?filename=np53JWU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnp53JWU.png&h=6afe3096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdJru4KBgyjhu7GKgehoCk3zkCi446Z28dSv46HjL8Mxb?filename=cHgVz3C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcHgVz3C.png&h=a215ea5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaKaq4qy5RbrcE89wWD7aT5tVDvAqNPDQZqNR1c8L1AJh?filename=U0tAz3F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0tAz3F.png&h=a55daa91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用jack線嘅jack in黎表達音樂感染力<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcPc521aF1vxnNV97GSBZbz8JjvN9oeVsS9fnUcNt7hyW?filename=7OtQo3s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7OtQo3s.png&h=f7369bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaT5jR6QwNTxquvyaUzUpmdgSF3kCWpkfFSJgXo9G9kG4?filename=VYkOU8J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVYkOU8J.png&h=170cd5b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXTHtxFXCPpVSFLgJ3fCCGMcTg9xZYY2d2m1PdtrxWTfV?filename=qeknZzM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqeknZzM.png&h=6ede7a76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeuSeq9HXgstaFT2A4HceScYMYmLmYJpgTZFxnXBvmXnJ?filename=F1t5cUQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1t5cUQ.png&h=ae5f21ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當中大部分畫面係連一句台詞都冇，可見作者分鏡同畫面表達嘅功力<br />\n<br />\n呢套漫畫係比中意音樂同曾經有音樂夢嘅你有再一次嘅感動，希望你仲可以發出你內心靈魂嘅吶喊"},{"pid":"a0b096302f7c917863c854cade200da7b0a2aec7","tid":2510304,"uid":350642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"有意睇 謝謝樓主"},{"pid":"1804ca8f2f542088d7329ae7053eb960e49521c0","tid":2510304,"uid":227815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:38:21.000Z","msg":"睇係幾好睇<br />\n但成日都要跳同埋每次都係用大跨頁兼極度浮誇演出黎做情感渲染<br />\n個人覺得好易睇到審美疲勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89a6c2969ee9234fb3e7d9baee561deb286c8c3","tid":2510304,"uid":235939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T05:49:00.000Z","msg":"補充<br />\n<br />\n另外有一套講jazz同saxophone 追夢漫畫blue giant都好好睇<br />\n大家有興趣可以追埋"}]}